description:
Filled with the flavor of fresh apples delicately seasoned with cinnamon and surrounded with a chewy whole grain cereal crust, these new Little Bites Snackin’ Bites are a delicious new “pop in your mouth” bite-sized snack that are perfect for any snacking occasion, even for a quick breakfast on the go! Made with a whole grain cereal crust and packed with delicious natural fruit filling, these delicious new “pop in your mouth” bite-sized snacks are a good source of Calcium, Vitamin D and Fiber. They contain no artificial flavors, colors, preservatives or trans fat.
Each box contains five pre-portioned and portable pouches containing six individual Snackin’ Bites pieces per pouch.
